  {
   "type": "title2",
   "html": "1911 － 健在"
  },
  {
   "type": "raw",
   "tag": "div",
   "attrs": {
    "class": "name"
   },
   "html": "\n[ せじま・りゅうぞう ]"
  },
  {
   "type": "raw",
   "tag": "div",
   "attrs": {
    "class": "prof"
   },
   "html": "\n関東軍参謀、大本営参謀本部部員、伊藤忠商事副社長・会長・相談役、陸軍中佐"
  },
  {
   "type": "raw",
   "tag": "table",
   "attrs": {
    "class": "lt"
   },
   "html": "<tbody><tr><td class=\"lt\"><a href=\"03s.html\">一覧　（サ）</a></td><td class=\"lt\"><a href.html\"=\"\">　</a></td><td class=\"lt\"><a href=\"http://www.amazon.co.jp/exec/obidos/redirect?link_code=ur2&amp;tag=click20thcetu-22&amp;camp=247&amp;creative=1211&amp;path=external-search%3Fsearch-type=ss%26index=blended%26keyword=%25E7%2580%25AC%25E5%25B3%25B6%2520%25E9%25BE%258D%25E4%25B8%2589\" target=\"_blank\">本を入手</a><img src=\"http://www.assoc-amazon.jp/e/ir?t=click20thcetu-22&amp;l=ur2&amp;o=9\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"border:none !important; margin:0px !important;\"></td><td class=\"lt\"><a href.html\"=\"\">　</a></td></tr></tbody>"
  },
  {
   "type": "raw",
   "tag": "div",
   "attrs": {
    "class": "off"
   },
   "html": "<span class=\"m_r\">エピソード 1</span>調査中。"
  },
  {
   "type": "timeline",
   "rows": [
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　富山県出身。陸士44期卒、陸大主席卒。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　<a href=\"../1941/12hawai.html\">太平洋戦争開戦</a>前から<a href=\"../1945/08gyoku.html\">終戦</a>の年まで参謀本部部員として主に作戦・用兵を担当。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　関東軍参謀として大陸で<a href=\"../1945/08gyoku.html\">終戦</a>を迎え、11年間のシベリア抑留生活を送る。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　帰国後、伊藤忠商事で辣腕を振るい、社の総合商社化にも貢献。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　中曽根ブレーンの一人として臨時行政改革推進審議会会長を務める。"
      }
     ]
    }
   ]
  },
  {
   "type": "timeline",
   "rows": [
